"title": "5332: harp",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5332: harp",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Early origins of the harp</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:19-Gen4:21\">GEN 4:19–4:21</a></strong> <em>Jubal was descended from Cain and was in the seventh generation after Adam.</em></p>\n<h2>The harp used in worship</h2>\n<h3>In joyous religious celebrations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:2-2Sam6:5\">2SA 6:2–6:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:6-1Chr13:8\">1CH 13:6–13:8</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:28\">1CH 15:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:27-2Chr20:28\">2CH 20:27–20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:27\">NEH 12:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:4\">PSA 49:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:1-Ps137:4\">PSA 137:1–137:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:32\">ISA 30:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:23\">AMO 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:2-Rev14:3\">REV 14:2–14:3</a></p>\n<h3>In temple worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:12\">2CH 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:12\">1KI 10:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:11\">2CH 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:16\">1CH 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:21\">1CH 15:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:5\">1CH 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr25:1\">1CH 25:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr25:3\">1CH 25:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr25:6\">1CH 25:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:25\">2CH 29:25</a></p>\n<h3>Associated with praising God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:4\">PSA 43:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:2\">PSA 33:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:7-Ps57:8\">PSA 57:7–57:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:22\">PSA 71:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:1-Ps81:2\">PSA 81:1–81:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:1-Ps92:4\">PSA 92:1–92:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:4-Ps98:6\">PSA 98:4–98:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:1-Ps108:2\">PSA 108:1–108:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:7\">PSA 147:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:3\">PSA 149:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:3\">PSA 150:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:8-Rev5:10\">REV 5:8–5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:2-Rev15:4\">REV 15:2–15:4</a></p>\n<h3>In pagan worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:7\">DAN 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:5\">DAN 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:10\">DAN 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:15\">DAN 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>The harp used to elicit divine inspiration</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:15-2Kgs3:19\">2KI 3:15–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:5-1Sam10:6\">1SA 10:5–10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:10\">1SA 18:10</a></p>\n<h2>The harp used to relieve depression</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:23\">1SA 16:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:16\">1SA 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:9-1Sam19:10\">1SA 19:9–19:10</a></p>\n<h2>The harp in secular use</h2>\n<h3>In joyous celebrations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:27\">GEN 31:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:12\">JOB 21:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:12\">ISA 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:11\">ISA 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:8\">ISA 24:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:13\">EZK 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:5-Amos6:6\">AMO 6:5–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:22\">REV 18:22</a></p>\n<h3>At times of mourning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:11\">ISA 16:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:31\">JOB 30:31</a></p>\n<h3>By prostitutes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:16\">ISA 23:16</a></strong></p>",
